OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780931474
OL,3,C83 arrests made at 'successful'
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FPolice have made 83 arrests at this
OL,7,Fyear's Appleby Horse Fair - down from
OL,8,F123 in 2025.
OL,10,FThe fair is the largest annual
OL,11,Fgathering of the Gypsy and Traveller
OL,12,Fcommunities, and had a "calm and
OL,13,Fcordial atmosphere," police said.
OL,15,FThe RSPCA says it is investigating
OL,16,Fafter a horse died in "suspicious
OL,17,Fcircumstances" on Saturday.
OL,19,FDet Sup Dan St Quintin said the
OL,20,Fweekend was "Successful from a police
OL,21,Fpoint of view."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
