OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780931474
OL,3,C83 arrests made at 'successful'
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FHe said: "We've had some really
OL,7,Fproactive and preventative arrests
OL,8,Fthat have taken place, but overall
OL,9,Farrest rates are down by 40 compared
OL,10,Fto last year.
OL,12,F"The significant proportion are still
OL,13,Fdrug driving and driving-related
OL,14,Foffences."
OL,16,FLive facial recognition cameras were
OL,17,Fused for the first time at the fair
OL,18,Fthis year, scanning people's faces to
OL,19,Fcheck if they match photos on the
OL,20,Fpolice's watchlists.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780931474
OL,3,C83 arrests made at 'successful'
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,FDet Sup St Quintin said: "We've
OL,7,Fscanned 56,000 faces over the four
OL,8,Fdays we've deployed this capability,
OL,9,Fand we've had three positive hits from
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,F"One of those led to an arrest for
OL,13,Ftheft of a male from Kendal, and the
OL,14,Fother two highlighted registered sex
OL,15,Foffenders from Cumbria who came to the
OL,16,Ffair - they weren't in any breach of
OL,17,Fconditions, but we still kept an eye
OL,18,Fon them.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780931474
OL,3,C83 arrests made at 'successful'
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,F"The feedback from the local community
OL,7,Fand the Gypsy, Roma and Traveller
OL,8,Fcommunity is that they say that (live
OL,9,Ffacial recognition) has put people off
OL,10,Fcoming, who we might not have come to
OL,11,Fthe fair in the first place."
OL,13,FThe RSPCA says it believes a horse
OL,14,Fdied in "suspicious circumstances" on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,17,FLyndsey Taylor, RSPCA Chief Inspector,
OL,18,Fsaid: "There was a mark on the horse's
OL,19,Fleft hind quarter, which we think may
OL,20,Fbe a trader's mark that's been altered
OL,21,Fto hide it.
OL,26,@pD@apmqD@Spn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780931474
OL,3,C83 arrests made at 'successful'
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,F"It was a reasonably healthy horse
OL,7,Fotherwise, but there's reason to
OL,8,Fsuspect that it's suspicious and we're
OL,9,Fmaking further investigations.
OL,11,F"There's hundreds of horses here, and
OL,12,Fit does need to be celebrated, those
OL,13,Fthat are really well looked after,
OL,14,Fthere are some very happy, healthy
OL,15,Fhorses here.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1780931474
OL,3,C83 arrests made at 'successful'
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair
OL,6,F"Obviously my team are dealing with
OL,7,Fthe other side of that, we will have
OL,8,Fsome people that need some advice and
OL,9,Feducation with regards to animal
OL,10,Fwelfare concerns, and that's what
OL,11,Fwe're here to do."
OL,13,FThe Appleby Horse Fair runs from
OL,14,FThursday 4 June to Wednesday 10 June,
OL,15,Fwith most of the fair packing down
OL,16,Fafter the Sunday.
OL,18,FDrivers in Cumbria have been warned to
OL,19,Fbe careful of slow moving horse drawn
OL,20,Fvehicles as they leave the county.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
